Use the standard library
This is how to minSubArraySum of nums:
   Remember that current is item 0 in nums
   Remember that best is item 0 in nums
   Remember that i is 1
   Do this (diff of nums's length and 1) times:
      Remember that x is item i in nums
      Remember that extended is sum of current and x
      When x is less than extended, then:
         Remember that current is x
      But, if not:
         Remember that current is extended
      End when
      When current is less than best, then:
         Remember that best is current
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is best
Now you know

>>> minSubArraySum of [2, 3, 4, 1, 2, 4]
1
>>> minSubArraySum of [-1, -2, -3]
-6
>>> minSubArraySum of [2, 3, 4, 1, 2, 4]
1